90628221-288d-4a70-8427-fcc2b0030a15	contact_page_content	{"heroTitle":"Contact Us","heroSubtitle":"Ready to embark on your luxury Egyptian adventure? Our specialists are here to craft your perfect journey.","getInTouchTitle":"Get In Touch","getInTouchSubtitle":"Whether you're planning your dream vacation or have questions about our services, we're here to help.","locationTitle":"Our Location","locationDetails":["EGYPT - CAIRO","Serving all of Egypt"],"emailTitle":"Email Us","emailDetails":["travel@iluxuryegypt.com "],"phoneTitle":"Call Us","phoneDetails":["Local: +201121012676","Local: +201061083190"],"hoursTitle":"Business Hours","hoursDetails":["24/7 Concierge Service","Sunday - Thursday: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM","Friday - Saturday: 10:00 AM - 4:00 PM"],"whyChooseTitle":"Why Choose iLuxury Egypt ","whyChooseItems":[{"title":"Bespoke Experiences","description":"Every journey uniquely crafted to match your personal preferences, dreams, and travel aspirations perfectly."},{"title":"24/7 Concierge","description":"Round-the-clock expert support ensuring seamless assistance throughout your entire Egyptian luxury journey."},{"title":" Expert Knowledge","description":"Deep local expertise unlocking exclusive access to Egypt's most treasured hidden wonders and experiences."}]}	2026-02-13 01:40:22.918	73480e9b-4af4-4782-9d1d-a7269fc854e2
2a03790c-d1c4-4694-88dc-32e444b5d1a3	your_experience_page_content	{"heroSubtitle":"CRAFTED FOR THE DISCERNING","heroTitle":"What Sets Us Apart","heroDescription":"\\nThe difference between a trip and a transformation.","heroImage":"https://iluxuryegypt.com/api/assets/uploads/f9be7cb5-d377-4c56-b67a-eee751e12ede.webp","introTitle":"The I.LuxuryEgypt Standard","introText":"even pillars of excellence. One unforgettable journey.","experiences":[{"icon":"Crown","title":"Absolute Privacy","description":"The Pyramids at dawn. Empty. Yours. Museum galleries after closing. Private temple dinners by candlelight. Egypt without the crowds only the magic.","highlights":["Monuments before opening, after closing","Curators open private collections","Temple access others can't arrange","Your timeline, not theirs"],"image":"https://iluxuryegypt.com/api/assets/uploads/8994e48c-b7ec-4fed-846f-e2fe7a4bd8ed.webp"},{"icon":"Users","title":"Select Company","description":"Twelve guests maximum. Carefully matched. The kind of travelers who elevate conversations over dinner and share your appetite for the extraordinary.","highlights":["Never more than 12 travelers","Shared curiosity, elevated taste","Access individuals can't access","The intimacy of private, the energy of shared"],"image":"https://iluxuryegypt.com/api/assets/uploads/1b441ddc-202b-4c9c-82a7-20cadb19fbf3.jpeg"},{"icon":"BookOpen","title":"PhDs, Not Scripts","description":"Egyptologists who've excavated tombs and published research. They don't recite facts they reveal secrets. Every site becomes a revelation.","highlights":["Doctorate-level expertise only","Published scholars and archaeologists","Conversations, not lectures","Available exclusively to you"],"image":"https://iluxuryegypt.com/api/assets/uploads/1d106306-8f82-4b26-bcff-8fa8dd7a0be9.jpg"},{"icon":"Hotel","title":"Legendary Properties","description":"Where Agatha Christie wrote. Where Churchill planned. Where history lives in the walls. Each stay chosen for character, service, and stories worth keeping.","highlights":["Historic icons, not hotel chains","Boutique sanctuaries with soul","Desert camps under infinite stars","Intimate Nile vessels, never cruise ships"],"image":"https://iluxuryegypt.com/api/assets/uploads/8a4d6a54-aab1-48f1-9982-f6af96047162.jpg"},{"icon":"UtensilsCrossed","title":" Culinary Insider Access","description":"Family kitchens that don't advertise. Rooftop chefs who've mastered ancient recipes. Markets where locals shop. Food as cultural immersion.","highlights":["Private chefs in extraordinary settings","Street food with insider guides","Cooking with Egypt's masters","Flavors tourists never taste"],"image":"https://iluxuryegypt.com/api/assets/uploads/15a0fd5c-410c-477e-b8be-8d0ecc3eab25.jpg"},{"icon":"Landmark","title":"Behind Closed Doors","description":"Active excavations. Academic symposiums. Master artisans in their workshops. The Egypt of scholars and creators accessible only through the right connections.","highlights":["Archaeological sites in progress","Private lectures, leading experts","Ancient crafts from master artisans","Access that requires introduction"],"image":"https://iluxuryegypt.com/api/assets/uploads/3138a261-3b9a-4a52-acc5-381ff1bee1d7.jpg"},{"icon":"Heart","title":"Entirely Bespoke","description":"Your pace. Your interests. Your needs anticipated before you voice them. Built from scratch around you never adapted from a template.","highlights":["Every detail personalized","Dietary and accessibility needs met seamlessly","Multi-generational or romantic perfectly balanced","Special passions accommodated completely",""],"image":"https://iluxuryegypt.com/api/assets/uploads/61638831-93bc-4c4c-94f0-8d4cfe1ece11.jpg"}],"summaryTitle":"The Details We Handle","summaryDescription":"So your only decision is what to marvel at next.","summaryCards":[{"title":"Frictionless Travel","description":"Private airport reception. All transfers arranged. Luggage handled door-to-door. Documentation managed."},{"title":"Truly All-Inclusive","description":"Site admissions. Guide gratuities. Refreshments on every excursion. Nothing unexpected. Nothing extra."},{"title":"Personal Attention","description":"Welcome gifts chosen for you. Custom journey books. Surprise moments throughout. Details that delight."}],"ctaButtonText":"Begin Your Journey"}	2026-02-14 20:08:28.357	73480e9b-4af4-4782-9d1d-a7269fc854e2
06232949-d466-4833-aec3-25fe2430eb51	iluxury_difference_page_content	{"heroSubtitle":"WHERE EXCELLENCE MEETS AUTHENTICITY","heroTitle":"Egypt. Elevated.","heroDescription":"Private access to 5,000 years of history. Zero compromises. Limited to 50 discerning travelers annually.","heroImage":"https://iluxuryegypt.com/api/assets/uploads/8994e48c-b7ec-4fed-846f-e2fe7a4bd8ed.webp","introTitle":"Why Discerning Travelers Choose Us","introText":"We accept fewer than 50 clients annually. Each journey is designed from scratch by our founder native Egyptian with over a decade curating experiences for Fortune 500 executives, celebrities, and ultra-high-net-worth families from the United States.\\n\\nNo group tours. No rigid schedules. No waiting in lines.","differences":[{"title":"Truly Bespoke","subtitle":"YOUR VISION, PERFECTED","description":"Your journey. Designed from scratch. No templates. No compromises.","features":["Private PhD Egyptologist (not a tour guide)","After-hours access to temples and tombs","Flexible itineraries change plans anytime","Recent example: Private Philae Temple dinner under the stars"],"image":"https://iluxuryegypt.com/api/assets/uploads/8994e48c-b7ec-4fed-846f-e2fe7a4bd8ed.webp"},{"title":"Egyptian Soul, Global Excellence","subtitle":"AUTHENTIC HERITAGE, WORLD-CLASS SERVICE","description":"We're Egyptian. We know the secrets. Trained by Ritz-Carlton and Four Seasons. We deliver both.","features":["Private museum viewings before opening","Access to palaces not on any map","Relationships with Egypt's finest chefs and historians","98% American clientele we know what you expect"],"image":"https://iluxuryegypt.com/api/assets/uploads/32c4a1f7-3fd5-4dc1-a6db-03a0a3a38ede.jpg"},{"title":"Luxury in Every Detail","subtitle":"WHERE EXCELLENCE IS STANDARD","description":"The details you'll never think about. Because we already did.","features":["Egypt's finest hotels (Old Cataract, Four Seasons)","Private vehicles (Mercedes S-Class, Range Rover, yachts)","Michelin-level dining at exclusive venues","White-glove customs walk through Cairo like a diplomat"],"image":"https://iluxuryegypt.com/api/assets/uploads/c3ac60e3-1990-4211-9b0f-67bbee200669.jpg"},{"title":"24/7 Support. Zero Stress.","subtitle":"TRAVEL WITHOUT WORRY","description":"Your dedicated team monitors everything. You stay present in the moment.","features":["Direct WhatsApp access (10-minute response guarantee)","Comprehensive insurance (medical, evacuation, cancellation)","Discreet security for high-profile clients","100% satisfaction. Zero unresolved issues. Ever."],"image":"https://iluxuryegypt.com/api/assets/uploads/60763aa0-61e4-4f11-95eb-9e1b79c2e9df.jpg"}],"whyItMattersTitle":"Why Discerning Travelers Choose Us","whyItMattersText":"We accept fewer than 50 clients annually. Each journey is designed personally by our founder a native Egyptian trained by the world's finest luxury brands.\\n\\nOur clients include Fortune 500 executives, celebrities, and families who expect perfection.\\n\\nNo group tours. No rigid schedules. No waiting. Ever."}	2026-02-20 14:00:29.498	73480e9b-4af4-4782-9d1d-a7269fc854e2
