8547e0af-4ece-446e-b16a-37ed36a3937f	Nile-View Luxury Suites	{"Wake to panoramic views of the legendary Nile from your private luxury suite. Our exclusive riverfront accommodations feature floor-to-ceiling windows overlooking Egypt's iconic waterway, where traditional feluccas sail past connecting ancient history with modern luxury Egypt accommodations.","Every suite features premium 600-thread-count Egyptian cotton linens, Italian marble bathrooms with soaking tubs and rainfall showers, plus private balconies perfect for sunset views. Enjoy Egyptian wine or handcrafted cocktails prepared by your personal butler available 24/7.","Experience Nile magic from your luxury sanctuary where modern amenities meet timeless wonder. Premium suites showcase authentic artifacts, museum-quality Egyptian furnishings, and design honoring 5,000 years of heritage delivering world-class comfort rivaling the finest luxury Egypt accommodations worldwide."}	Start Your Nile Journey Here	/egypt-nile-cruise-tours	{https://iluxuryegypt.com/api/assets/uploads/1bfd6d3f-6529-4454-a29a-d790e638b745.jpg,https://iluxuryegypt.com/api/assets/uploads/dae06c85-6ccd-4ae9-983a-d10451bd842f.jpg,https://iluxuryegypt.com/api/assets/uploads/761a1b18-a909-46d1-802b-592d6dd97790.jpg,https://iluxuryegypt.com/api/assets/uploads/66ea30a0-6f1f-411c-af83-eb32e1f785a5.jpg}	2026-02-04 13:04:12.39
