rant before crossing back to the East Bank. Explore the vast Karnak Temple complex, connected to Luxor Temple by the ancient Avenue of Sphinxes. Wander through the Great Hypostyle Hall with its 134 towering columns, sacred lake, and numerous chapels and sanctuaries. Return to Aswan by evening, arriving at your hotel with memories of Luxor's grandeur."}]	{"Aswan "," Luxor "," Valley of the Kings "," Karnak Temple "," Hatshepsut Temple"}	ASWAN	f	t	2026-02-14 00:38:45.887862	2026-02-14 00:47:54.192	73480e9b-4af4-4782-9d1d-a7269fc854e2	\N
