uryegypt.com/api/assets/uploads/b1cfa672-6fce-4363-b85f-51e838cc5a92.jpg,https://iluxuryegypt.com/api/assets/uploads/d9e52917-8d02-4767-a855-5996eb1b6026.jpg,https://iluxuryegypt.com/api/assets/uploads/06da9b61-2516-4f0f-8736-fc0740268072.jpg}	 8 Days / 7 Nights	2 - 8 	Challenging	0	USD	{"Meet-and-assist service by our representatives at airports","All transfers by private air-conditioned 4x4 vehicles","1 night accommodation at Four Seasons Hotel Cairo at Nile Plaza","1 night accommodation at Desert Lodge, Bahariya","2 nights accommodation at Desert Camp, White Desert","3 nights accommodation at Siwa Eco-Lodge","All entrance fees to temples and protected desert areas mentioned in the itinerary","Services of a desert expert guide throughout your trip","All meals stated in the itinerary – (B) for breakfast, (L) for lunch, (D) for dinner","Daily meditation sessions","Stargazing session with professional astronomer","Cultural workshops (pottery, palm weaving, or natural dyeing)","Camel ride at Siwa Oasis","Bottled water during all tours and meals","24/7 on-call support","All applicable taxes and VAT"}	{"International flights to and from Cairo","Gratuities for guides, drivers, and lodge staff","Alcoholic beverages","Personal expenses and souvenirs","Travel insurance"}	[{"day": 1, "title": "Day 1 | Cairo – Gateway to Desert Mysteries", "activities": [], "description": "Arrive at Cairo International Airport. Our meet-and-assist service will take you through the passport control area, assist with your luggage and customs, and transport you to your hotel in Cairo overlooking the Nile. Evening dinner at the hotel.\\nOvernight: Four Seasons Hotel Cairo at Nile Plaza (D)"}, {"day": 2, "title": "Day 2 | Bahariya Oasis – Desert Journey Begins", "activities": [], "description": "After breakfast, drive to Bahariya Oasis in the Western Desert. The journey takes approximately 4 hours through changing desert landscapes. Check in at your desert lodge and enjoy the afternoon at leisure. Evening meditation session before dinner.\\nOvernight: Desert Lodge, Bahariya (B, L, D)"}, {"day": 3, "title": "Day 3 | White Desert – Surreal Landscapes & Stargazing", "activities": [], "description": "Early morning departure to the White Desert to see the sunrise among the chalk rock formations. Your guide will explain the geological history of this unique landscape. Enjoy a guided walk through the rock formations before lunch. Afternoon free for personal reflection or journaling. Evening stargazing session with a professional astronomer.\\nOvernight: Desert Camp, White Desert (B, L, D)"}, {"day": 4, "title": "Day 4 | Black Desert – Energy Walks & Crystal Mountains", "activities": [], "description": "After breakfast, visit the Black Desert where volcanic rocks contrast with the golden sand. Continue to the Crystal Mountain where quartz crystals cover the ground. Your guide will lead a walking meditation through these areas. Afternoon free for yoga or personal reflection. Dinner at the camp.\\nOvernight: Desert Camp, White Desert (B, L, D)"}, {"day": 5, "title": "Day 5 | Siwa Oasis – Palm Groves & Serenity", "activities": [], "description": "After breakfast, check out and drive to Siwa Oasis near the Libyan border. The drive takes approximately 6-7 hours. Check in at your eco-lodge and enjoy a walk among the palm groves. Visit Cleopatra's Spring before dinner featuring local Siwan cuisine.\\nOvernight: Siwa Eco-Lodge (B, L, D)"}, {"day": 6, "title": "Day 6 | Temple of Oracle & Cultural Immersion", "activities": [], "description": "After breakfast, visit the Temple of the Oracle where Alexander the Great is said to have consulted the oracle. Your guide will explain the temple's history and significance. After lunch, participate in cultural workshops with local artisans learning traditional pottery, palm weaving, or natural dyeing techniques. Evening camel ride across the dunes at sunset.\\nOvernight: Siwa Eco-Lodge (B, L, D)"}, {"day": 7, "title": "Day 7 | Siwa – Salt Lakes & Desert Contemplation", "activities": [], "description": "Full day exploring Siwa's Salt Lakes. Walk along the shores and enjoy meditation sessions in this peaceful setting. Optional visit to the hot springs known for their mineral-rich waters. Afternoon free for additional activities or rest. Evening farewell dinner with traditional Bedouin music.\\nOvernight: Siwa Eco-Lodge (B, L, D)"}, {"day": 8, "title": "Day 8 | Return to Cairo – Departure", "activities": [], "description": "After breakfast, drive back to Cairo. Depending on your flight schedule, you may have time for last-minute activities before your transfer to Cairo International Airport for departure.\\n(B)"}]	{Cairo,Bahariya,"White Deser","Black Desert","Siwa Oasis"}	Wellness & Cultural Journeys 	f	t	2026-01-19 21:17:11.167376	2026-02-13 01:46:32.009	73480e9b-4af4-4782-9d1d-a7269fc854e2	https://iluxuryegypt.com/api/assets/uploads/44510eac-a854-49ec-aeb3-5fe008cbbaaa.pdf
