hat would have stood 42 meters tall and weighed approximately 1,200 tons if completed. Your guide will explain ancient stone-cutting techniques and why this monument was abandoned due to cracks. Take a scenic motorboat ride to Agilkia Island to explore the magnificent Philae Temple, dedicated to the goddess Isis. Admire beautifully preserved Ptolemaic reliefs, towering columns, and intricate hieroglyphics. Learn how UNESCO relocated this temple stone by stone. Enjoy lunch before returning to Luxor."}]	{"Luxor "," Aswan "," High Dam "," Philae Temple "," Unfinished Obelisk"}	LUXOR	f	t	2026-02-13 23:05:58.264274	2026-02-14 00:28:58.558	73480e9b-4af4-4782-9d1d-a7269fc854e2	\N
